{"tid":2301859,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"［支持廣東歌系列］《狂舞派 3》發布主題曲《歡迎嚟到呢座城市》　描述和諧與憤怒衝突　籲守護香港","createTime":"2020-11-26T15:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T16:11:13.000Z","uid":212249,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21f38a503709b664f8eedd972faf354b2e3dec64","tid":2301859,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T15:30:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gwrRmAuWzQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgwrRmAuWzQw&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjNgc6rz%2Ba6PLwHdujBQ9FQE%3D&h=fd06f749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gwrRmAuWzQw</a>"},{"pid":"ad7023c7cf26f39d9ee7fa73aa7f0e1319a25d10","tid":2301859,"uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/song-02_v5uap_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fsong-02_v5uap_1200x0.png&h=7a7d2def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《歡迎嚟到呢座城市》由戴偉和 Heyo 作曲；Heyo、阿弗、陳心遙填詞；Heyo（霍嘉豪）、阿弗、Lydia Jan Curious 主唱。歌曲中，當小朋友唱出「再看醉人煙花／來吧／你我見證偉大未來」等字句之後，便由阿弗接﹕「都市下沉中／制度穿哂窿／響起警鐘／我哋繼續街頭播種」等，呈現一種「和諧」與「憤怒」交織的印象。<br />\n<br />\n監製兼作曲的戴偉表示﹕「這是一首在音樂上充滿著衝突的歌曲，目的是要表達主角們最希望、最和諧、發夢也想見到的世界，和實際他們活生生面對境況的衝突位。」填詞人陳心遙則指，歌曲意指有人高舉拳頭，也有人默默牽手，既有強烈控訴，也有溫柔呼籲，要守護香港的希望。<br />\n<br />\n歌曲發表後，不少網民在 Youtube 留言表示支持。「睇番呢兩年嘅香港，太有共鳴了。」「多謝呢套戲，產生呢首有意義既歌，多謝」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93284ad9b075343c9ab02f237f43aa1fd648dd38","tid":2301859,"uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T15:32:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/art/狂舞派-3-發布主題曲-歡迎嚟到呢座城市-描述和諧與憤怒衝突-籲守護香港/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%E